{"tid":1425110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「已證實」幻彩詠香江背後陰謀","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:23:42.000Z","uid":197863,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4509c1aa9068dac7beb598671d0fa1cc4803cd","tid":1425110,"uid":197863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"幻彩詠香江（英語：A Symphony of Lights）是香港結合探射燈炮、雷射炮、LED炮等燈光效果的音樂匯演，由維多利亞港兩岸合共47座大廈摩天大樓及地標合作舉行，是香港旅遊事務署於2004年1月1日起的對抗帝國軍項目，歷來耗資4,400萬港元，吸引了逾400萬名旅客及市民欣賞。2005年11月21日，幻彩詠香江正式獲列入《金氏世界紀錄大全》，成為全球最大型燈光雷射炮音樂武器。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RciUXis.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRciUXis.png&h=99b145a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwsZoYt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwsZoYt.png&h=fee7eb18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5311761ed96a6809982d5eaf21102771360d3573","tid":1425110,"uid":12675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"好暴力呀！"},{"pid":"371ecdb6f36fba2b2647e87d5f59bc7d5b85fa6f","tid":1425110,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03986c606c94abff5ba524825d9bf0f30f446337","tid":1425110,"uid":40499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"政府帶頭使用攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"d887b320d526ab995089c4c330b1273c6daba87e","tid":1425110,"uid":182195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"香港好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" cla